ã€Total of TOTAL 90ã€
In collaboration with Nike, the art book Total of TOTAL 90 captures everything about Nikeâ€™s legendary â€˜Total 90â€™ series. From the concept and design details of Total 90, to an archive of 90 iconic jerseys and a special editorial, this book brings together all three pillars of the Total 90 legacy in one comprehensive artistic collection.

1. TOTAL 90 : The Total 90 series is an iconic line in the history of Nike Football products. It debuted in 2004 and was used until 2006, undergoing various small and large evolutions with diverse features during that time. In this book, we have summarized the overall concept and main characteristics of the Total 90 jersey in a broad framework.

2. 90 Archives of Total 90 : Honoring the great legacy of Nike Footballâ€˜s Total 90â€”which continues to provide so much inspiration and influenceâ€”we have gathered a total of 90 archives, as the name suggests. From the most symbolic and representative jerseys to the unique and rare ones that graced stadiums around the world, a total of 90 Total 90 archive pieces have been carefully selected and included.

3. Editorial : Nikeâ€™s Total 90 brought a design revolution to football jerseys. These groundbreaking and audacious jerseys, even 20 years later, have been reinterpreted as a lifestyle fashion on the streets of 2025. Through a collaboration between the football creative brand â€˜Over the Pitchâ€™ and Koreaâ€˜s top model agency â€™Gost,â€˜ the creative direction of â€™Over the Pitchâ€˜ and the models from â€™Gost FCâ€˜ have captured the Total 90 jerseys in an editorial photoshoot.
